Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《哥谭》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Gotham...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说阿卡姆疯人院放你出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard they let you out of Arkham.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我正常了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. I'm sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是以利亚·范·达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Elijah Van Dahl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯瓦尔德·科波特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Oswald Cobblepot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是格特鲁德的亲人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're related to Gertrud?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没告诉我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She never told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Told you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I had a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有父亲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐的大家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A big, happy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是梦  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a dream, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  平克尼警官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Officer Pinkney.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶器是一根撬棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Murder weapon was a crowbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面有你的指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your fingerprints were on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被人陷害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈登警探被判有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Detective Gordon guilty on all counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能不陪在我们身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you not be with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Birthdays...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and first steps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦破膝盖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and skinned knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得去别的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始新生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  别这样  我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim, don't do this! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your feet! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Step out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Line it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向右转  走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Face right! Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熄灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lights out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熄灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lights out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得出列\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人戈登  请出列\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prisoner Gordon, step out of line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几周来你都没惹什么麻烦  戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Several weeks with no incidents, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到  据说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not what I expected. Word was you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个惹事精\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想好好服刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to do my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该转移你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's time to move you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F区  "世界的尽头"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F Wing. "World's End."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通囚区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}General population.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该不会很惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This should not come as a surprise to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护性监禁只是暂时的特权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protective custody is just a temporary privilege,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不适用于你那么长的刑期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one which can't be sustained for a sentence as long as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你正在等待上诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you have an appeal pending,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  我可以延长这个安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in which case I can prolong this arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定挺难受的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's got to sting just a little, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人都抛弃了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your people seem to have abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被判犯下谋杀罪有其坏处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being convicted for murder has its downsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要烦恼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't fret so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在F区肯定能见到许多老相识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you'll see a lot of familiar faces over in F Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多人还是你自己逮捕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many of which you arrested yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报复时间到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一记倒挂金钩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here comes the flying scissor kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That one wasn't mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能证明自己合群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you show yourself to be a team player,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你合群吗  戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you a team player, Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了传达我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I forgot to pass on my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好友的问候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}good friend's regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前局长洛布向你问好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ex-Commissioner Loeb says hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵守规则  或许你还能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow the rules, and perhaps you'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违反规则  你肯定活不下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Break them, and you most certainly won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这一区叫做"世界的尽头"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's why they call this wing World's End.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这里大多数人来说  这里就是尽头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For most here, it's exactly that, the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only way out:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假释或被装进尸袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}parole or a body bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没有人获准假释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nobody gets parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的  我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}It's true. I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得一清二楚  一个鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear as day-- a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个穿着黑长裙的苍白的老女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was this pale old woman in a long black dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你离我那么近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时什么反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尖叫着跑开了  还用说吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I ran away screaming, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信有鬼吗  奥斯瓦尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, do you believe in ghosts, Oswald?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这栋房子里有好几个呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This house has several of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别担心  它们都挺友好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't worry, they're all quite friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别听他胡说  这里没有鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't listen to him. There are no ghosts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是有鬼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, there's ghosts, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房子是我爷爷建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This house was built by my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死在这儿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妻子和他两个姐妹也是在楼上过世的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His wife and two sisters also passed away upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我可怜的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my poor dear parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}many ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩是怎么认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个无聊的故事  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a boring story, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来说吧  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, let me tell it, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母亲去世后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After my mother died,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这房子里独自待了好几个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sat alone in this house for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  我几乎不下床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barely got out of bed, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终  我找到了一间离这里不远的餐厅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finally, I found a diner, not too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天同一时间去那里  点同样的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd go there every day at the same time, order the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡汤和苏打水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chicken soup and a seltzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝是我的服务员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grace was my waitress,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I grew very fond of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和我讲了她两个可怜孩子的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She told me of her two poor children,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨莎和查尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sasha and Charles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲他们如何受他们父亲的虐待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how they suffered at the hands of their abusive father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须帮她  我向她提供庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to help. I offered her refuge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她接受了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是这栋房子里再次有了欢声笑语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this house heard laughter once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一切就顺其自然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then one thing led to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情萌发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love blossomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成了如今这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是我唯一的血亲  奥斯瓦尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you are my only true blood relative, Oswald.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my poor dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你伤到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you hurt at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没有  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. I'm-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨手笨脚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clumsy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-家庭  -敬家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Family. - To family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹特  他们把他转到普通囚区了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dent, they got him in general population now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F区  你知道那意味着什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F Wing. You know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们送进去的人都关在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone we've ever put away is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别老是这句话  你总会有办法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop saying that! There's always something you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重审\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A retrial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是让他转狱也行  老天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or have him transferred to another prison, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就继续这么做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what, just keep doing what you always do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真凶不知在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's wasting away in that place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃着甜甜圈  逍遥快活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while the real killer's out there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他却在那里日渐憔悴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}eating donuts and getting laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The real killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶器上的指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fingerprints on the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆是清白的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没杀平克尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't kill Pinkney.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, gee, um, that's... unfair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的健康状况不允许我喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My health forbids me from drinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少我能看着你享用这瓶雪利酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but at least I can watch you enjoy this sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我父亲生前最爱喝的酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was my father's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那是我曾祖父曼弗雷德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that's my great-grandfather Manfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多年前  他在哥谭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He started a small tailor's shop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开了一家小裁缝店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in Gotham many, many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为城市精英制作西装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made suits for the city's elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲像他的哥哥们那样做了学徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father became an apprentice like every son before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你也做了学徒吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You were an apprentice, too? - I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还相当有天赋呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had rather a flare for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜没那个命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it was not to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲病倒之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When my father succumbed to illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母亲把我留在身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my mother held me close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在家接受教育\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homeschooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她认为有必要保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She felt a need to protect me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受到城市里的诱惑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the temptations of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间以来  我不敢问你母亲的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this time, I've been afraid to ask about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我抛弃了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry I abandoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果当初我知道我还抛弃了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had I known I was also abandoning you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dear God,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个胆小的笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}such a cowardly fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这辈子过得快乐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she have a happy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从未伤害过任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She never hurt a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有时不太孝顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was not always a good son,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她从未责备过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she never spoke a word of reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时不孝顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not always a good son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很难相信呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I find that hard to credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这么体面的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An nice young man like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干过很多坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都有罪  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all sinners, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该吃药了  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time for your medicine, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生开的治心脏的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doctor gave them to me for my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心驶得万年船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人探视  戈登先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}You have a visitor, Mr. Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不要回禁闭室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm not going back to the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保证过的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是典狱长要转移你的  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The warden's the one who's moving you. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好的可不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wasn't our agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你听着  这不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you listen! This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了这间牢房  这是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I paid for this cell! This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交易还挺多的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of business going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,典狱长能分一杯羹吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The warden get a cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要这童子军周末前死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want the Boy Scout dead by week's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你气色不错啊  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look good, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方挺适合你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This place agrees with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我也该进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'll check in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,减几斤肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lose a few pounds, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄个酷文身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get a cool tat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不非得来看我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't need to check up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开玩笑呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的笑脸是我一周里最开心的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Highlight of my week to see your smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我和丹特谈过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I spoke to Dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有意重新开启案子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's looking into reopening the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不能惹事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you got to keep your nose clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别因为管不住脾气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last thing you can do is do more time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被加刑  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause you lost your temper, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没那么难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, shouldn't be that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的人看起来都挺和气的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone seems really nice around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找企鹅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm looking for Penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他有什么想说的没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See what he's got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他躲在什么地方避风头了  但别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's laying low someplace, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会找到他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱怎样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直在给我写信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been writing to me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几周前突然不再来信了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The letters stopped a few weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不想做告诉你这消息的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to be the one to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱的孩子没了  吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lee lost the baby, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她搬去南部了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She moved down south.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就再没人有她的消息了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's heard from her since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让这事击溃你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, don't let this beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴  哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to see you, Harv.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  我会救你出去的  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim, I'm gonna get you out of here, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  别让这事击溃你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim, don't let this break you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't give up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim! Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪  猪头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you going, pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟去年和几个人一起抢银行来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My little brother ran with a crew that pulled off a few bank jobs last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸上管他们叫红头罩帮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papers called them the Red Hood Gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一枪打爆了我弟弟的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You put a bullet in my brother's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让外面的朋友去看看她好不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about I have my friends on the outside pay her a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她知道她错过了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show her what she's been missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真惨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guys, cool it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cool it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peace, peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别插手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  戈登先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, Mr. Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧  好了  各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got this. Now, come on now, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都深呼吸一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just take a deep breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各回各的牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back to your cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪在原地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assume the position now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back it up! Back it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带犯人维弗去禁闭室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take inmate Weaver to the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个送去医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And these two to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来  起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up. Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  你听到长官的话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go. You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-父亲  -怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}- Father? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  你只是在梦游\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay. You were sleepwalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我父亲的办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  我给你搬把椅子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, let me, let me get you a chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  扶我回床上去吧  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, help me back to bed, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是控制病情的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're for my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏病吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心脏上有个洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a hole in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说还在不断扩大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It keeps getting bigger apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是我的心魔在吞噬它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think my demons are feeding on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有心魔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸  我有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadly, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕你也有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, too, I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多事没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's so much I haven't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多让我羞愧的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much that I'm ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前是个罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我造了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多孽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurt people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍心机  满口谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}manipulated, lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了谋权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了复仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀过人  父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've killed people, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的生活始于我在墓地遇见你的那一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our lives together started the moment I met you at the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎你的过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing before that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原谅你过去所有的罪过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I forgive you for all your past transgressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再纠结过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be free of them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里好好生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and live here in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们叫他们知道厉害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We showed them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  不管你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, uh, whatever your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Puck-- well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家都叫我帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but people call me Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我远点  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay away from me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈登警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Detective Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再是警探了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a detective anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比警探要厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're way more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个真正的英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a true hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two winters ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹被儿童绑架犯抓走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my little sister was abducted by child snatchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被掳走了三天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three days she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你找到了她  抓到了那群人渣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you found her and-and busted the scum that took her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了她  还救过很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saved her life and dozens of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是真英雄的作为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right there, that's a true hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是尽职而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一个姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个漂亮的姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我约她出来  她同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked her out and she said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很有格调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she was classy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让她坐公交\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't make her take the bus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我偷了辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I snatched a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是借\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算还回去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was gonna take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察不相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cops didn't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就进来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判了你几年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What they give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不少啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没法抱怨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I broke the law, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法律就是法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The law is the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会像我爷爷一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna be like my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死在了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He died in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了一段时间后就再不许我和父亲来看他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And wouldn't let me and my father visit him after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们后来还是来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But finally we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次见他时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last time I saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不一样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都认不出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't recognize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会落得那种下场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not gonna happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  先生  我不会死在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir, I won't die in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就离我远一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这俩犯人怎么还在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are these prisoners still doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上带他们回各自的牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get them to their cells immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯紧这家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And watch this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚失去了孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just lost a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让他很愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes him mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耳听四路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼观八方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一件你不知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know something you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是怎样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what kind of man you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elijah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐稳了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我们有一些坏消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid we have some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯今天去了公共图书馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles was at the public library today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我正在写的小说搜集资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Research for the novel I'm writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时在看一些旧报纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was reading some old newspapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了一件令人震惊的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I made an alarming discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯瓦尔德才不像他说的那么体面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oswald is not the nice young man he says he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们不是那么与世隔绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we didn't lead such sheltered lives here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会知道全世界都知道的真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we would know what the whole world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一名臭名昭著的罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a notorious criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been sheltering
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名杀人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都可能在自己的床上被人奸杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could have all been raped and murdered in our beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奸杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raped and murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫你企鹅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They call you the Penguin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说句公道话...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没强奸过谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I never raped anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是上天保佑  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, that's a mercy, now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子把他的过去告诉我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My son told me about his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是没说他有多出名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just didn't tell me how famous he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太谦虚了  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're too modest, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elijah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家里住个暴力罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a violent criminal in our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝  放松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grace, relax,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得救赎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Redeemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不是这种人了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not this man anymore, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how... h-how do you know? How do you know he's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我审视了他的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've looked into his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了他美丽的心灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen his beautiful heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"衣冠楚楚的黑社会头头"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The Dapper Gangland Kingpin."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:22:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B计划是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's plan B?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你独处一会儿  企鹅先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping to spend a little time with you, Mr. Penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. But, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我奥斯瓦尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}uh, please, call me Oswald.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.78,0:23:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是那个人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I'm not that man anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没剩下一点企鹅的影子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There isn't a little bit of Penguin left?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点坏小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A little bad boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我内心有个坏女孩呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a little bad girl in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你对那老头子有什么打算  我想加入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you've got planned for the old man, I want in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-加入  -我们可以有很大成就\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- In? - We could do great things, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:23:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose. I hadn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you and me work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以拥有一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we could have it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以把我妈妈和弟弟挤走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could squeeze my mom and brother out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为什么要那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我们就是一对儿疯狂乱套的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess we're just a couple of crazy mixed up kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制点自己  女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Restrain yourself, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我基本上是你哥哥了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm your practically your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.19,0:24:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没上钩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去试试吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I try?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我觉得他不是装的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I don't think he's faking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是傻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he's kind of simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.77,0:24:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈登  小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gordon. Watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维弗马上要从禁闭室出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Weaver's coming out the hole. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.65,0:25:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没什么事是合情合理的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing happens around here like it's supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.85,0:25:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的死期要到了  戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your day's coming, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.29,0:25:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.48,0:25:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你男朋友吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a look at your boyfriend over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.32,0:25:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Puck!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还有谁会帮你  猪头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's gonna help you now, pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢那样吗  戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you like that, Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.68,0:25:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.38,0:25:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别延长你的刑期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't extend your sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.14,0:26:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆没杀那孩子  我们都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim didn't kill that kid. We all know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.62,0:26:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是  是谁杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thing is, who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.44,0:26:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁陷害了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, who'd set him up that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他还能在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't know how much longer
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.51,0:26:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方支撑多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he can stay alive in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.96,0:26:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想求你帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I'm asking for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.60,0:26:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Funny, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.25,0:26:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全有权利叫我滚蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have every right to tell me to go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.20,0:26:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.71,0:26:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没别人可以求助了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got no one else to turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.93,0:26:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Harvey...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.46,0:26:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在室内戴帽子是很没礼貌的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's very rude to wear a hat indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.85,0:26:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这面料吗  是意大利的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You like the fabric? It's Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.13,0:27:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.41,0:27:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人可以靠衣着表现出自己很多方面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A man can say so much about himself by what he wears.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.53,0:27:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太赞同了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.76,0:27:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为当今穿衣随便的年轻人难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I weep for today's casual youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.37,0:27:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你提议我们做这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so glad you suggested we do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.99,0:27:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好久没做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.51,0:27:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.24,0:27:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.88,0:27:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.35,0:27:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁去叫医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have someone call for an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.54,0:27:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝  救命  格蕾丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grace! Help! Help, Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.69,0:27:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把以利亚怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you do to Elijah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.59,0:27:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没怎么啊  -救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nothing. - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.49,0:27:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就来  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coming, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.08,0:27:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这里收拾好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clean up this mess
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.76,0:27:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫医生来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and call the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.33,0:28:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.55,0:28:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺卖力啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hard at it, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.37,0:28:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你恢复我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for getting me my old job back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.10,0:28:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友帕克被打得不轻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your friend Puck is pretty banged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.39,0:28:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你去医务室看他  或许对他有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might do him some good if you were to come see him in the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.24,0:28:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.25,0:28:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是他的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.26,0:28:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他认为你是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He thinks you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.25,0:28:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子会死在这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kid's gonna die in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.61,0:28:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.18,0:28:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很快完事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.63,0:28:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.48,0:28:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.88,0:28:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说我有个血块还是什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They-they said I have a clot or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觉得晕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just feel seasick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你来看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.78,0:29:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Means a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.11,0:29:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定会好好照顾你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure they'll take good care of you in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.68,0:29:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你撑住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hang in there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.91,0:29:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.10,0:29:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...don't give up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你的难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel your sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.36,0:29:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.37,0:29:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得选择生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you got to choose life, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.08,0:29:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.89,0:29:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Choose life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.02,0:29:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.19,0:29:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, kid, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.23,0:29:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好起来了  你得吸取教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you get better, you learn the lesson here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.64,0:29:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我远远的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you stay the hell away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是英雄  也不是你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a hero and I'm not your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.41,0:29:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是个囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just a convict.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.44,0:30:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是电影之夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight's movie night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.13,0:30:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都聚在大堂  还关着灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone in the main hall together with the lights off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.39,0:30:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好准备就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.20,0:30:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的情况恶化了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}His condition has gotten worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.19,0:30:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个洞扩大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hole has gotten bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.38,0:30:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出现了感染\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now there's an infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给了他抗生素  能帮他补水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've given him antibiotics and rehydrated him,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.87,0:30:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但恐怕用处不大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I fear it will have little consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.52,0:30:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他该料理后事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time for him to get his affairs in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.22,0:30:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能时日无多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He may not have long.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.24,0:30:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去让他们给你做碗鸡汤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to have them make you some nice chicken soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.11,0:30:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要力气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.35,0:30:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.59,0:30:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.75,0:31:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别听医生的  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't listen to doctors, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.82,0:31:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾那么多次证明他们错了  都数不过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've proved them wrong so many times I've lost count.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.92,0:31:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我还能共度很多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I will have many more years to spend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.22,0:31:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.36,0:31:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但或许我们该找律师来谈谈  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But perhaps we should speak with my lawyer, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.77,0:31:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些事想跟他商谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have some things I'd like to go over with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.19,0:31:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几周来  发生了很多改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much has changed these past weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.88,0:31:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会叫他来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have him stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.13,0:32:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.45,0:32:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.99,0:32:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.50,0:32:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫律师了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's called for his lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他要修改遗嘱吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's going to change his will? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.29,0:32:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他死了  科波特就会得到应属于我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when he dies, Cobblepot will get what's rightfully ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.37,0:32:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识那老头子时  他憔悴不堪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That old man was a shriveled-up wreck when I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.55,0:32:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我让他重获青春  是我让他重焕生机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made him feel young again. I brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.38,0:32:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只臭老鼠又做过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what has this gutter rodent done?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.90,0:32:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩破棋盘游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Played stupid board games
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.46,0:32:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念叨他可怜的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and whined about his wretched mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.09,0:32:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只害虫必须走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That vermin has to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.93,0:32:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他喜欢这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he likes it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.36,0:32:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要怎么说服他离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can we persuade him to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.78,0:32:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠要怎么除掉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you get rid of rats?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-老鼠胶吗  -不是  傻帽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Glue traps? - No, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.69,0:33:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲好多了  但他在休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father is feeling much better, but he is resting,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.24,0:33:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今晚就不来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so he will not be joining us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.74,0:33:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.26,0:33:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们吃饭吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's eat, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.82,0:33:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.45,0:33:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是只漂亮的苍蝇  看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a pretty fly. Look, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.73,0:33:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  看啊  大家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah! Come on, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.55,0:33:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo, show's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.29,0:34:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.79,0:34:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢  他是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing? He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.19,0:34:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.72,0:34:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.14,0:34:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're dead. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.87,0:34:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.58,0:34:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了  猪头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're dead, pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.53,0:34:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要个尸袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna need a body bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.98,0:35:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布洛克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}Bullock?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.99,0:35:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.11,0:35:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我们是在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's it look like we're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.22,0:35:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把你弄出去  来吧  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're getting you out of here. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.80,0:35:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假血  可伸缩刀  居然真成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fake blood, retractable knife-- can't believe it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.34,0:35:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.53,0:35:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈维  如果我就该待在这里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harvey, what if this is where I'm supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.33,0:35:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  快走  -布洛克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?! Let's go! - Bullock...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.94,0:35:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.69,0:35:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嗑药了吗  很多好人为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you tripping? A lot of good men put their butts
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.32,0:35:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒了极大风险  我  他  法尔科内阁下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a live rail for you-- me, him, Don freaking Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.09,0:35:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而杀了平克尼的人现在还逍遥法外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}While walking around somewhere is the guy that killed Pinkney,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.63,0:35:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他陷害了你  破坏了你的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}framed you and destroyed your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:35:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逍遥法外  而你就站在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's walking around while you're standing there
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.36,0:36:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难过迷茫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all blue and misty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.25,0:36:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的自怨自艾  赶紧走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, screw your self-pity and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.13,0:36:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.28,0:36:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.76,0:36:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还需要你们帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I need one more favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.18,0:36:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.65,0:36:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈登警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Detective Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.12,0:36:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.17,0:36:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得尽量快  尽量轻地跟我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to move as quickly and quietly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.84,0:36:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-逃跑吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You mean, like, escaping? - Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.30,0:36:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但那是违法的  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But that's against the law. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.01,0:36:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了  选择生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like you said, choose life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.93,0:36:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早说的  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.33,0:36:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎么想  你就是个英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether you like it or not, you're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.59,0:36:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prisoner Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.52,0:36:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是死了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're supposed to be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.32,0:36:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一样意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm as surprised as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.43,0:36:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么活过来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What brought you back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.39,0:37:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-朋友  -朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Friends. - Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.26,0:37:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朋友真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.12,0:37:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你需要朋友的时候他们又不见了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But where are they when you need 'em, huh? Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.71,0:37:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉太爽了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, that felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.09,0:37:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉把你卷进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry I got you into all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑  从没觉得这么带劲过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you kidding? Never felt more alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.46,0:37:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠地揍我  弄得像点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, hit me hard, make it look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.04,0:37:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别揍牙  我才修过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just don't touch the teeth. I just had 'em fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你母亲啊  她当时多年轻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at your mother-- she was so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.91,0:37:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯瓦尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oswald.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.05,0:37:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  格蕾丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.45,0:37:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我骗了你  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lied to you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.17,0:37:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲并没有身体疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father was never physically ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.70,0:37:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是深陷忧郁症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He only suffered a deep melancholy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.32,0:38:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他内心充满黑暗的冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was plagued by dark impulses,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.27,0:38:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力的邪恶念头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}evil thoughts of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.22,0:38:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲说  他家族很多人都有这个毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother said many in his family had the same affliction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.22,0:38:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得那枪声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember the sound of the gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.62,0:38:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时在他房间外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was outside his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.10,0:38:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尖叫着让母亲去拿钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I screamed for my mother to get the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.37,0:38:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他手上尚有余温的枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the warm gun in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.10,0:38:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.47,0:38:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His face.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.01,0:38:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲叫我永远别提起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother said never to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.22,0:38:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼后数年  我们一直足不出户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For years after the funeral, we never left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.30,0:38:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想假装理解我父亲受的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't pretend to understand my father's torment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.01,0:38:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但或许你理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think perhaps you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.44,0:38:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替你难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.98,0:38:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I beg of you, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.62,0:38:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远别像他那样向痛苦屈服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never give in to the pain as he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.67,0:38:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.56,0:38:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.88,0:39:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳明天还会升起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the sun will come up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.03,0:39:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.12,0:39:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I feel like a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.82,0:39:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的身体不要紧吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.59,0:39:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To hell with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.29,0:39:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你拥有一切  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to have it all, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这栋房子  和里面的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This house and all that's in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.05,0:39:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都保持原样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it just the way it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.94,0:39:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件历史  我们的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a piece of history, our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.82,0:39:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥谭的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotham's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.41,0:39:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一早  我就会让律师起草文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First thing tomorrow, I'll have my lawyers draw it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.49,0:39:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.05,0:39:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -以利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, no! - Elijah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.03,0:39:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喝了那个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he... did he drink that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.58,0:40:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是啊  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. - Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.31,0:40:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不该喝的  萨莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not supposed to. Sasha,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.16,0:40:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫救护车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}call an ambulance. Call an am...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.08,0:40:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑住  父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay with us, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.97,0:40:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救护车就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.57,0:40:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.65,0:40:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们逃出来了  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We made it, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.04,0:40:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.26,0:40:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔科内阁下在黑门监狱有的是人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don Falcone had all the contacts inside of Blackgate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.20,0:40:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他策划了整件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He made this whole thing happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.40,0:41:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.01,0:41:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恐怕无以为报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure I can ever repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.35,0:41:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.12,0:41:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乐意帮助老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm happy to help an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.14,0:41:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.19,0:41:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.95,0:41:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两小时前我还是个死人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two hours ago, I was a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.09,0:41:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有人能帮你出国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have people that will get you out of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.38,0:41:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以在哥谭给你安排个安全的住处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or I can arrange a safe place for you in Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.35,0:41:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.01,0:41:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.46,0:41:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去找小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to go find Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.61,0:41:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就得先洗清我的罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to do that, I have to clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.63,0:41:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就得回哥谭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to do that, I have to go back to Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.44,0:41:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你有答案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So there's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.57,0:41:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里一部分想逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Part of me says, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.89,0:42:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呼吸到了新鲜空气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm breathing fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.41,0:42:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.18,0:42:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you run,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.50,0:42:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就得一直跑下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you've got to keep running.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.50,0:42:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有些人可以承受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.80,0:42:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个斗士  吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a fighter, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被打趴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got knocked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会一直趴着吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you stay down?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.22,0:42:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是重新站起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or do you get back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.70,0:42:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.30,0:42:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Puck?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.37,0:42:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我们都出来了  别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, we made it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.21,0:42:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. No. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.62,0:42:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.92,0:42:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Puck?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.19,0:42:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.70,0:42:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jim, he's gone.
